NK015(ba)022:1: gtor ma dang dgra bgegs dbyer med du bsam pa /
NK015(ba)022:3: rje btsun rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i dpal
NK015(ba)022:4: ldan bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka' bden pa
NK015(ba)022:5: dang / sangs rgyas kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK015(ba)022:6: chos kyi bka' dge 'dun gyi bka' bka' gsang sngags dang /
NK015(ba)022:9: phyag rgya ting nge 'dzin yi dam rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK015(ba)022:10: dam pa chos skyong ba'i srung ma rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK015(ba)022:11: bden pa chen po'i mthu stobs kyi /
NK015(ba)022:12: bdag cag dpon slob dgon sde grwa tshang mi nor 'khor dang bcas pa rnams la /
NK015(ba)022:13: nyi ma phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad nas /
NK015(ba)022:19: lag pa tshig tu rdo ba /
NK015(ba)022:21: sbyor ba rtsub mo shom pa /
NK015(ba)022:34: sa bla gar gnas gar yod kyang /
NK015(ba)022:36: pho nya lcags kyu can gyi snying nas bzung /
NK015(ba)022:37: zhags pa can gyi mgul nas chings /
NK015(ba)022:38: lcags sgrog can gyi yan lag sdom /
NK015(ba)022:39: dril bu can gyi myos su chugs /
NK015(ba)022:40: las kyi rlung nag chen po'i rgyab nas deng /
NK015(ba)022:41: 'jigs pa'i mun nag chen po'i mdun sus la /
NK015(ba)022:46: +aahmh'u sha yi ri bo khrag gi rgya mtsho /
NK015(ba)022:47: rus pa'i gram khrod nam mkha' dang mnyam par gyur /
NK015(ba)022:48: +aahmh'u brgyud pa'i bla ma yi dam gyi lha tshogs
NK015(ba)022:49: chos skyong srung ma rnams kyi zhal du dgra bgegs
NK015(ba)022:50: kyi ma h+aa mam sa la kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)022:53: sha rus khrag gsum la kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)022:54: rnam shes tshogs brgyad la kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)022:55: zhes phud kyi bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro chos skyongs mchod /
